nder -20 Championship, which will be held in Lima, Peru, starts two weeks after the end of the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1040, \"end\": 1044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lima_District\", \"score\": 0.9754286773823825, \"rank\": 0.024785695720825805, \"text\": \"Lima\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lima_District\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lima_District\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"-Paul A Reid  HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": []}]}"